divs: Sighting DetailsThese pictures were taken last night, this orb was hovering there just above the clouds for around 30mins or so. It would pulsate a bright golden color then dissapear and appear in the same spot. It also went from a bright light to a small dot then back again. I was watching it the whole time and in the middle of doing this it appeared to go very bright and 2 or 3 small lights appeared beneath almost as if they dropped from it. The pictures a high def so you can zoom in. Also i have noticed that every time i step outside late at night over the post few months there are a couple of light flashes noticeable to the eye, do you know anything about this? I have more pictures of the orb also.
Summary: UFO orb sighting 3/1/2012. Melbourne Australia- Pictures
